Package: HierBasis
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Regression and Sparse Additive Modeling
Version: 1.0.2
Date: 2018-07-18
Author: Asad Haris, Ali Shojaie and Noah Simon
Maintainer: Asad Haris <aharis@uw.edu>
Description: Nonparametric regression and high dimensional additive model via a
    convex hierarchical penalty. This package implements the methods presented in 
    Asad Haris, Ali Shojaie and Noah Simon (2016) <eprint arXiv:1611.09972>.
